msgid ""
"The size of each word. This should only be either `uint32` or `uint64`. "
"Strings (`'uint32'`, `'uint64'`) are fine. Note that requesting `uint64` "
"will draw twice as many bits as `uint32` for the same `n_words`. This is a "
"convenience for `BitGenerator`\\ s that express their states as `uint64` "
"arrays."
msgstr ""

